<!-- the abstract for the module. If not provided, the XSL will use the in scope -->
 <abstract>
    <li>Establishment of neutral assembly model within STEP is quite important and urgent issue from various application viewpoints, such as parametric assembly, assembly/disassembly process planning, kinematic analysis, and tolerance analysis. Features and their relationship play a key role to represent the relationship among the assembled components. This document is the draft technical specification of an application module for the product property feature definition and its relationships as a base of the features needed to represent the assembly model. </li>
 </abstract>

